<br>
Xena had recieved a message from Queen Maytha that seemed urgent,though it didn't explain much of anything,the two left immediatly.<br>
<br>
Once in the tribe,Xena dismounted Argo II,helped Eve off her own horse,then took the two steeds and put them in the stables.<br>
<br>
&quot;Come on Eve.&quot; She motioned to Eve,and lead the way to Maytha's hut.<br>
<br>
She knocks on the Queens hut door and awaits an answer. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenmaytha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Maytha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(8/22/02 2:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/amznqnmay/smallmaytha.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Xena &amp; Eve arrive in Sarmatia</span><hr size=1> Maytha was waiting on top of the ceremonal stage near her hut. &quot;Im over here Xena...im glad you both came...&quot; She said. Then looked at Eve...&quot;Eve Your Under Arrest for the Murder of The Amazon Varia&quot; Maytha said, saddened. Guards come and grabs Eve, and they begin to chain her... <p><FONT SIZE="10"><FONT FACE="WingDings">Z</FONT>
